Motherboard is physical the physical arrangement in a computer that contains the
computer's basic circuitry and components.

the computer components included in the motherboard are:

The microprocessor
(Optionally) coprocessors Memory
basic input/output system (BIOS)
Expansion slot
Interconnecting circuitry


SMP is processing of programs by multiple processors that share a common
operating system and memory.

